      "author": "Ekrizdis367",
      "description": "## Summary\n\n- Fix combo blocks with multiple `loop:` / `break:` pairs rendering as one merged loop\n- Each `loop:` header now starts a separate loop diagram; `break:` items attach to the preceding loop segment\n- README updated to document multiple loop blocks\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] Open a combo with setup `steps:` followed by Loop → Break → Loop → Break (e.g. Chromatic Orrery combo from issue #3)\n- [ ] Confirm two separate loop diagrams with their own \"Break out\" sections\n- [ ] Confirm single loop/break combos still render correctly\n- [ ] Confirm `line:` variants with loop/break still work",
