      "author": "Ekrizdis367",
      "description": "## Features\n- Add optional `(SET) NUMBER` syntax on decklist lines to pin a card to a specific Scryfall printing (e.g. `1 Ancient Den (MRD) 278`), matching Moxfield/MTGO export style. Hover/tap previews use that exact printing; lines without a specifier behave as before.\n\n## Fixes\n- Specific-printing fetches are cached only under their printing key, not the plain card name, so name-only lookups still resolve Scryfall's default printing.\n- Pending async fetches dedupe using the shared `printingKey()` helper for consistency with cache lookups.\n\n## Contributors\n- @alexboydray — specific printing support (PR #4)",
      "downloadCount": 1,
